text:
Dolly Parton was inoculated on Tuesday (Mar 2) with the #Covid19 #vaccine that she helped to fund. 

The country music legend adapted one of her best-known songs ‘Jolene’ before getting the Moderna jab at Vanderbilt University in Nashville.
